message.body: Are you working????
I tried calling but no answer :( I love you! Hopefully you get to call me.
Sorry i missed you! Heading to work! Can i call at like...11?
Yeah!!! I'll be falling asleep so probably won't be able to talk long :)
Hi baby! Just asked my sister and she said that it is on Friday. Charles made the wrong date for the reservation. Haha. So it's Friday, Feb. 20th.
Excellent!!!
:D yayayayayay! And I'll buy my tickets for v-day :)
IM GONNA SKIP MY CLASSSSSSSS!!!!!!!!
Okay. So I will get to you around 3 (hopefully earlier) and I am leaving Sunday at 3:10. I chose the cheapest tickets :D
Oh tis wonderful news, darling :) Thank you thank you!! I'll buy my tix for Bday!
It's done!
Woohoooo!
So...what is we doing for Your bday?? I wont have class that friday either hah
O_O me neither! Cause it's spring break for me. I'm spending t with my baby!!
Wooo! I feel guilty...cause yo friends gonna want you!! But woo!!
They can have us on Saturday. Friday is for you and me exclusively!!
I coming to philly then??
Me likes "exclusively" haha. Greedy us
:D I love the exclusivity of us. Haha. If you want.
Or I can go to you.
Would you hate me if i said i dont want to take off that much work? I dont want to pull you away from everyone on bday tho

:) tis okie dokie my love. Would you be mad if instead of spending the entire week, I came on wed or thurs? And stayed until Sunday? I believe I'll have to get some work done so I wanted to have that mon and tues to do it.
Thats perfectly fine! But only if you let me dwell in your bedroom during My spring break...and Easter! :) Pretty please
:DDDD yesssss!
Although, tues and wed are sucky cause I'll be at nova all day. Thurs I'm done at 10 and mon and fri I'm done at 1:20.
Hahah yeeees. And i ... I cant say i mind. I will follow youuuu follow you where ever you may goooooo. Fa lalala la la laa laaaaa. I'll visit you at school :-p
Have we even been back on campus together?? Dont even remember haha
Nope! It's been too long! Yayayay I'm happy. You made my day!
I almost wanna go and buy my ticket now. Haha.
Ahahah i bought mine for february :-D Thanks for making me smile big before bedtime. Happy dream time haha

Hahah. I lied! Coming home on Sunday is more expensive than coming home on Saturday. So can I go to you on Tuesday and come back on Saturday? Is that bad?
Have a good sleep!
Noooothing is bad, my love. They are days with you! It is perfect. Totally perfect. And i will :) Just one more nice cup of tea and then bed :)
Heheh. Okay! Then I'm going to buy it right now!!!!!!!!!!
Holy moly!! You gone crazay!! When i wake up, i'll buy my tix for spring and easter too woo! Going wild for Spring and Holy break!!
YAYAYAYAYAYAY. Hahah. Holy break.
Oh it's gonna be good, baby, promise.
I believe it!!! Go to bed. Goodnight!
Sweet daydreams, my love!
PS. 2 Cups of tea, though they were beyond delicious...was a horrible choice...
Haha. Can't sleep now? Boo!
Hehe nope :) Kinda loopey
Go to bed!!
Haha i am in bed!!
Come here!!
I come I come!!
No lab :D
